      "content": "The logs strongly suggest your `/api/v1/checkout/complete` endpoint is timing out when trying to communicate with the `payment-gateway-auth` service. This intermittent behavior during peak traffic points toward resource exhaustion or throttling on the payment gateway side, or perhaps within your own service infrastructure. You should investigate the health and latency of `payment-gateway-auth` under load, as its response time is likely exceeding your 10-second timeout threshold. Consider implementing circuit breakers or exponential backoff on your retry logic to handle these transient failures more gracefully.",
